-- Dent, Faulk, Sabol, Sanders, Sharpe Named to Pro Football Hall of Fame
-- B y   M i c h a e l   S i l l u p
-- 2011-02-06T00:37:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-06/dent-faulk-sabol-sanders-sharpe-named-to-pro-football-hall-of-fame.html
Cornerback  Deion Sanders  and running
back Marshall Faulk were named to the Pro Football Hall of Fame
in their first year of eligibility.  Also named at a press conference in  Dallas  were Richard
Dent, Shannon Sharpe, Chris Hanburger, Les Richter and NFL Films
founder Ed Sabol.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michael Sillup in Dallas at 
 msillup@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
